Same voltage for each 18650 ass a single cell (3.7v), but if you know where to look, you can get ones up to 4000mah. For their size, they #8217;re much better than NiMh and Lipo. I have 6 and don #8217;t even go through all of them in one day.

Yeah they #8217;re rechargeable. On amazon they go for about $10 each. I use Geteed 3,000 mah 40/60Amp high drain batteries. Many Li Ion batteries on amazon are fakes (will advertise 8,000 mah but will only be 1,000-1,500. The highest charge possible with 18650 #8217;s right now is 3,500mah) but the Geteed ones are actually rated as advertised. Also, make sure that you get high drain 18650 #8217;s (20 amps at least). Most fuses in stock AEGs are from around 25-30A, so make sure that your power source can supply that.
